;[exp] WAY == "s"

[texton]
[リーダー f=06]「...!」[k]
Suddenly, I sensed something moving behind me![k]
[textoff]
@wait time=500
@walk turn=n
@wait time=500
[texton]
When I hurriedly turned around, monsters attacked me![k]
[textoff]
@monster pos=0 name=アネモネ
@monster pos=1 name=アネモネ
@monster pos=2 name=アネモネ
